(12, 'Optional Activity Package', 'Optional Activity Package - Dominican Republic', '3b334v', '<h3>About</h3>\r\n\r\n<p class="about">\r\n	In addition to the five included activities in the ISV Dominican Republic adventure tour, ISV is pleased to offer participants traveling to the Dominican Republic this exciting Optional Activity Package (OAP). These activities are more of the best that the Dominican Republic has to offer in outdoor adventure and appreciation of the spectacular natural surroundings. Each year about 95% of participants choose the ISV Optional Activity Package as it adds such great value to the overall experience. All activities in the package will be organized by ISV staff prior to arrival, which ensures availability so that a participant wonâ€™t miss out. All participants have to do is show up and be ready to have a great time!\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<div id="contents" class="twocolumn">\r\n\r\n	<h2>The ISV Dominican Republic OAP includes:</h2>\r\n	\r\n<!-- ACCORDION IMAGE ROTATOR -->\r\n<div id="js-accordion">\r\n\r\n	<!-- slide 1 -->\r\n	<div id="slide1" class="accordionImgDiv">\r\n		<a href="index.html" id="slideimg1" class="accordionSlideImage asyncImgLoadAccordion" title="/img/oap/dominican_republic/accordion/1.jpg|White Water Rafting, Jarabacoa|This whitewater activity takes place on the rapids of the Yaque del Norte River nearby to the mountain adventure capital of the Caribbean, Jarabacoa! This action-packed rafting trip will take participants through extremely fun, technical Class IV rapids and breathtaking scenery in one of the most remote areas of the Dominican Republic."></a>\r\n		<div class="accordionDescBack"></div>\r\n		<div class="accordionDesc">\r\n			<p class="accordionDescHeader">Jarabacoa</h3>\r\n			\r\n		</div>                    \r\n		<div class="slideStrip" title="/img/oap/dominican_republic/accordion/1strip.jpg"></div>\r\n		<p class="slideDesc">Jarabacoa</p>  \r\n	</div>\r\n											  \r\n	<!-- slide 2 -->\r\n	<div id="slide2" class="accordionImgDiv"> \r\n		<a href="index.html" id="slideimg2" class="accordionSlideImage asyncImgLoadAccordion" title="/img/oap/dominican_republic/accordion/2.jpg|Canyoning, Cabarete|From the Caribbean coastal town of Cabarete we will travel to the beautiful mountain area of Damajagua to the 27 waterfalls. We will hike through a tropical forest to the base of a waterfall, then journey through a canyon for an adventure that involves hiking, cliff jumping and sliding down natural waterslides in an amazing jungle setting. Even Tarzan would be jealous! Enjoy lunch in a pristine setting. Hike out again through tropical forests."></a>\r\n		<div class="accordionDescBack"></div>\r\n		<div class="accordionDesc">\r\n			<p class="accordionDescHeader">Cabarete</h3>\r\n			\r\n		</div>                    \r\n		<div class="slideStrip" title="/img/oap/dominican_republic/accordion/2strip.jpg"></div>\r\n		<p class="slideDesc">Cabarete</p> \r\n	</div>\r\n					\r\n	<!-- slide 3 -->\r\n	<div id="slide3" class="accordionImgDiv">\r\n		<a href="index.html" id="slideimg3" class="accordionSlideImage asyncImgLoadAccordion" title="/img/oap/dominican_republic/accordion/3.jpg|Los Haitises National Park, Samana|Arrive in the town of Samana in the eastern Dominican Republic and admire its African heritage and colorful streets. Travel across Samana Bay by boat to the spectacular Los Haitises National Park; a pristine maze of egg-shaped, small islands and mangroves formed by limestone erosion. Visit a spectacular cave where the Taino Indians lived. Kayak through red mangroves, floating by spectacular fauna and flora. This is a unique opportunity to see one of the most secluded and exotic parks in the Dominican Republic."></a>\r\n		<div class="accordionDescBack"></div>\r\n		<div class="accordionDesc">\r\n			<p class="accordionDescHeader">Samana</h3>\r\n			\r\n		</div>                    \r\n		<div class="slideStrip" title="/img/oap/dominican_republic/accordion/3strip.jpg"></div>\r\n		<p class="slideDesc">Samana</p>  \r\n	</div>\r\n							  \r\n	<!-- slide 4 -->\r\n	<div id="slide4" class="accordionImgDiv">\r\n		<a href="index.html" id="slideimg4" class="accordionSlideImage asyncImgLoadAccordion" title="/img/oap/dominican_republic/accordion/4.jpg|Hike to the House of Tarzan|Hike along tropical forest and across a crystalline river where you will learn about endemic flora and fauna and local coffee initiatives. Arrive at Tarzanâ€™s House, a secluded terraced hide- away in the jungle with its own private waterfall. There you will have a relaxing swim in an amazing setting and afternoon snack. This is one unique place you do not want to miss!"></a>\r\n		<div class="accordionDescBack"></div>\r\n		<div class="accordionDesc">\r\n			<p class="accordionDescHeader">Hike</h3>\r\n			\r\n		</div>                   \r\n	   <div class="slideStrip" title="/img/oap/dominican_republic/accordion/4strip.jpg"></div>\r\n	   <p class="slideDesc">Hike</p>  \r\n	</div>               \r\n	\r\n	<!-- slide 5 -->\r\n	<div id="slide5" class="accordionImgDiv">\r\n		<a href="index.html" id="slideimg5" class="accordionSlideImage asyncImgLoadAccordion" title="/img/oap/dominican_republic/accordion/5.jpg|Windsurfing, Cabarete|Arrive in the multicultural and world- famous adventure community of Cabarete. Learn to windsurf on one of the best beaches in the world for this sport. Cabarete has a large bay protected by a reef; ideal for learning. Friendly professional staff will help participants to grasp the basics. A unique opportunity to learn a great sport in a tropical setting!"></a> \r\n		<div class="accordionDescBack"></div>\r\n		<div class="accordionDesc">\r\n			<p class="accordionDescHeader">Cabarete</h3>\r\n			\r\n		</div>    \r\n		<div class="slideStrip" title="/img/oap/dominican_republic/accordion/5strip.jpg"></div>\r\n		<p class="slideDesc">Cabarete</p>  \r\n	</div>   \r\n	\r\n</div> <!-- accordionContainer -->\r\n\r\n<!-- ACCORDION CONTROL PANEL -->   \r\n<div id="accordionControlPanel">\r\n<span id="accorControlBtnDesc"></span>\r\n	<img id="accorBackBtn" class="accorControlButton ie6PNGfix" src="img/slider/accordion/control/back.png" alt="" /><img \r\n	id="accorPlayBtn" class="accorControlButton ie6PNGfix" src="img/slider/accordion/control/pause.png" alt="" /><img \r\n	id="accorForwardBtn" class="accorControlButton ie6PNGfix" src="img/slider/accordion/control/forward.png" alt="" /> \r\n</div> <!-- accordionControlPanel -->      \r\n	\r\n	<div id="ImageTitle">White Water Rafting, Jarabacoa</div>\r\n	<div id="ImageDescrip">Learn to surf from local expert instructors in a world renowned location for surfing. This two hour lesson will teach you the basics and hopefully have you &quot;hanging ten&quot; in no time.</div>\r\n</div>			', '', '2010-06-01 18:01:23', '2010-06-01 18:01:23', '', '', 0, '', 0),
(13, 'Optional Activity Package', 'Optional Activity Package - New Zealand', '35h35h', '<h3>About</h3>\r\n\r\n<p class="about">\r\n	In addition to the five included activities in the ISV New Zealand adventure tour, ISV is pleased to offer participants traveling to New Zealand this exciting Optional Activity Package (OAP). These activities are more of the best that New Zealand has to offer in outdoor adventure and discovery of the culture and spectacular natural surroundings. Each year about 95% of participants obtain the OAP as it adds such amazing value to the overall experience. All activities in the package will be organised by ISV staff prior to your arrival, which ensures availability so that you wonâ€™t miss out on these popular activities. All you have to do is show up and be ready to have a great time!\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<div id="contents" class="twocolumn">\r\n\r\n	<h2>The ISV New Zealand OAP includes:</h2>\r\n	\r\n<!-- ACCORDION IMAGE ROTATOR -->\r\n<div id="js-accordion">\r\n\r\n	<!-- slide 1 -->\r\n	<div id="slide1" class="accordionImgDiv">\r\n		<a href="index.html" id="slideimg1" class="accordionSlideImage asyncImgLoadAccordion" title="/img/oap/new_zealand/accordion/1.jpg|The Black Abyss â€“ Black Water Rafting (Waitomo)|The Black Abyss is an exhilarating five hour extravaganza which is a more challenging upgrade to the ISV included black water rafting activity. Imagine this: enter the caves by abseiling deep down into the vast limestone cavern. Then you will find yourself climbing underground waterfalls, jumping off rocks into the water and zip-lining in the dark across the glow worm lit river. This is caving at its most exciting!"></a>\r\n		<div class="accordionDescBack"></div>\r\n		<div class="accordionDesc">\r\n			<p class="accordionDescHeader">The Black Abyss</h3>\r\n			\r\n		</div>                    \r\n		<div class="slideStrip" title="/img/oap/new_zealand/accordion/1strip.jpg"></div>\r\n		<p class="slideDesc">The<br />Black<br />Abyss</p>  \r\n	</div>\r\n											  \r\n	<!-- slide 2 -->\r\n	<div id="slide2" class="accordionImgDiv"> \r\n		<a href="index.html" id="slideimg2" class="accordionSlideImage asyncImgLoadAccordion" title="/img/oap/new_zealand/accordion/2.jpg|Franz Josef Glacier Hike (Franz Josef)|An incredible glacier experience with phenomenal photo opportunities. Start the adventure with a stunning hike along the beautiful valley floor to the foot of the glacier. Gaining confidence as you go and with a total of up to 6 hours on the ice you could find yourself in all manner of situations, from squeezing through tight blue crevasses to sliding through ice caves. Along the way you will learn about the creation, melt and movement of this ice giant! Travel to spectacular icefalls in the mid reaches where expert guides use step-cutting techniques to make this extensive and challenging trip surprisingly achievable."></a>\r\n		<div class="accordionDescBack"></div>\r\n		<div class="accordionDesc">\r\n			<p class="accordionDescHeader">Tsitsikamma National Park</h3>\r\n			\r\n		</div>                    \r\n		<div class="slideStrip" title="/img/oap/new_zealand/accordion/2strip.jpg"></div>\r\n		<p class="slideDesc">Glacier<br />Hike</p> \r\n	</div>\r\n					\r\n	<!-- slide 3 -->\r\n	<div id="slide3" class="accordionImgDiv">\r\n		<a href="index.html" id="slideimg3" class="accordionSlideImage asyncImgLoadAccordion" title="/img/oap/new_zealand/accordion/3.jpg|Zorb! (Rotorua)|Zig, Zag Zorb! Youâ€™ve seen it on â€œThe Amazing Raceâ€ â€“ now experience this unique kiwi activity for yourself! Slip, slide and tumble down a track inside an enormous inflated plastic ball with two of your new best friends up to the speed of 50km per hour. Guaranteed fun and laughter like youâ€™ve never had before!"></a>\r\n		<div class="accordionDescBack"></div>\r\n		<div class="accordionDesc">\r\n			<p class="accordionDescHeader">Rotorua</h3>\r\n			\r\n		</div>                    \r\n		<div class="slideStrip" title="/img/oap/new_zealand/accordion/3strip.jpg"></div>\r\n		<p class="slideDesc">Rotorua</p>  \r\n	</div>\r\n							  \r\n	<!-- slide 4 -->\r\n	<div id="slide4" class="accordionImgDiv">\r\n		<a href="index.html" id="slideimg4" class="accordionSlideImage asyncImgLoadAccordion" title="/img/oap/new_zealand/accordion/4.jpg|Maori Cultural Performance and Hangi Dinner (Rotorua)|Spend an evening learning about Maori customs, rituals, beliefs, and language through song, dance and performance before enjoying an authentic â€œHangiâ€ (ground cooked feast). You will have the chance to experience a formal Maori welcome (Powhiri) and see a â€œHakaâ€ (traditional Maori war challenge) in an authentic and powerful presentation of Maori Culture! An experience not to be missed."></a>\r\n		<div class="accordionDescBack"></div>\r\n		<div class="accordionDesc">\r\n			<p class="accordionDescHeader">Rotorua</h3>\r\n			\r\n		</div>                   \r\n	   <div class="slideStrip" title="/img/oap/new_zealand/accordion/4strip.jpg"></div>\r\n	   <p class="slideDesc">Rotorua</p>  \r\n	</div>               \r\n	\r\n	<!-- slide 5 -->\r\n	<div id="slide5" class="accordionImgDiv">\r\n		<a href="index.html" id="slideimg5" class="accordionSlideImage asyncImgLoadAccordion" title="/img/oap/new_zealand/accordion/5.jpg|Shotover Jet (Queenstown)|Hold on tight and experience the thrills of jet boating by twisting and turning at breathtaking speeds through the narrow Shotover river canyons, flying fast past rocky outcrops and spinning 360 degrees in the open areas. Find out what a jet boat can really do Kiwi style!"></a> \r\n		<div class="accordionDescBack"></div>\r\n		<div class="accordionDesc">\r\n			<p class="accordionDescHeader">Queenstown</h3>\r\n			\r\n		</div>    \r\n		<div class="slideStrip" title="/img/oap/new_zealand/accordion/5strip.jpg"></div>\r\n		<p class="slideDesc">Queenstown</p>  \r\n	</div>   \r\n	\r\n</div> <!-- accordionContainer -->\r\n\r\n<!-- ACCORDION CONTROL PANEL -->   \r\n<div id="accordionControlPanel">\r\n<span id="accorControlBtnDesc"></span>\r\n	<img id="accorBackBtn" class="accorControlButton ie6PNGfix" src="img/slider/accordion/control/back.png" alt="" /><img \r\n	id="accorPlayBtn" class="accorControlButton ie6PNGfix" src="img/slider/accordion/control/pause.png" alt="" /><img \r\n	id="accorForwardBtn" class="accorControlButton ie6PNGfix" src="img/slider/accordion/control/forward.png" alt="" /> \r\n</div> <!-- accordionControlPanel -->   \r\n	\r\n	<div id="ImageTitle">The Black Abyss â€“ Black Water Rafting (Waitomo)</div>\r\n	<div id="ImageDescrip">The Black Abyss is an exhilarating five hour extravaganza which is a more challenging upgrade to the ISV included black water rafting activity. Imagine this: enter the caves by abseiling deep down into the vast limestone cavern. Then you will find yourself climbing underground waterfalls, jumping off rocks into the water and zip-lining in the dark across the glow worm lit river. This is caving at its most exciting!</div>\r\n</div>			', '', '2010-06-01 18:01:41', '2010-06-01 18:01:41', '', '', 0, '', 0),
(14, 'Optional Activity Package', 'Optional Activity Package - South Africa', '6j6h46h', '<h3>About</h3>\r\n\r\n<p class="about">\r\n	In addition to the five included activities in the ISV South Africa adventure tour, ISV is pleased to offer participants travelling to South Africa this exciting Optional Activity Package (OAP). These activities are more of the best that South Africa has to offer in outdoor adventure and appreciation of the spectacular natural surroundings. Each year about 95% of ISV participants choose the ISV Optional Activity Package as it adds such great value to the overall experience. All activities in the package will be organized by ISV staff prior to arrival, which ensures availability so that a participant won''t miss out. All participants have to do is show up and be ready to have a great time!\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<div id="contents" class="twocolumn">\r\n\r\n	<h2>The ISV South African OAP includes:</h2>\r\n	\r\n<!-- ACCORDION IMAGE ROTATOR -->\r\n<div id="js-accordion">\r\n\r\n	<!-- slide 1 -->\r\n	<div id="slide1" class="accordionImgDiv">\r\n		<a href="index.html" id="slideimg1" class="accordionSlideImage asyncImgLoadAccordion" title="/img/oap/south_africa/accordion/1.jpg|Jeffreys Bay: Surfing Lessons|Learn to surf from local expert instructors in a world renowned location for surfing. This two hour lesson will teach you the basics and hopefully have you &quot;hanging ten&quot; in no time."></a>\r\n		<div class="accordionDescBack"></div>\r\n		<div class="accordionDesc">\r\n			<p class="accordionDescHeader">Jeffreys Bay</h3>\r\n			\r\n		</div>                    \r\n		<div class="slideStrip" title="/img/oap/south_africa/accordion/1strip.jpg"></div>\r\n		<p class="slideDesc">Jeffreys<br />Bay</p>  \r\n	</div>\r\n											  \r\n	<!-- slide 2 -->\r\n	<div id="slide2" class="accordionImgDiv"> \r\n		<a href="index.html" id="slideimg2" class="accordionSlideImage asyncImgLoadAccordion" title="/img/oap/south_africa/accordion/2.jpg|Tsitsikamma National Park: Entrance Fee and Guided Waterfall Hike|Explore the rugged coastline of Tsitsikamma National Park. Take a three hour hike along the oceanâ€™s edge to a waterfall that flows right into the sea. Swim in a tannin coloured pool at the foot of the waterfall and do some cliff jumps if you are brave enough to experience the &quot;refreshing&quot; water!"></a>\r\n		<div class="accordionDescBack"></div>\r\n		<div class="accordionDesc">\r\n			<p class="accordionDescHeader">Tsitsikamma National Park</h3>\r\n			\r\n		</div>                    \r\n		<div class="slideStrip" title="/img/oap/south_africa/accordion/2strip.jpg"></div>\r\n		<p class="slideDesc">Tsitsikamma<br />National<br /> Park</p> \r\n	</div>\r\n					\r\n	<!-- slide 3 -->\r\n	<div id="slide3" class="accordionImgDiv">\r\n		<a href="index.html" id="slideimg3" class="accordionSlideImage asyncImgLoadAccordion" title="/img/oap/south_africa/accordion/3.jpg|Cape Town: Hike/Cable Car and Abseil from Table Mountain|Experience the iconic Table Mountain through an adrenaline adventure like no other. Hike three to four hours to the top or take the Cable Car to the summit. From there, gather your courage as we abseil 112 m (336 ft) down the highest commercial abseil in the world! Professional abseiling instructors will help you face your fears in a safe environment."></a>\r\n		<div class="accordionDescBack"></div>\r\n		<div class="accordionDesc">\r\n			<p class="accordionDescHeader">Cape Town</h3>\r\n			\r\n		</div>                    \r\n		<div class="slideStrip" title="/img/oap/south_africa/accordion/3strip.jpg"></div>\r\n		<p class="slideDesc">Cape <br />Town</p>  \r\n	</div>\r\n							  \r\n	<!-- slide 4 -->\r\n	<div id="slide4" class="accordionImgDiv">\r\n		<a href="index.html" id="slideimg4" class="accordionSlideImage asyncImgLoadAccordion" title="/img/oap/south_africa/accordion/4.jpg|Cape Town: Moyo Dinner and Cultural Show|Top off your cultural day in Cape Town with an evening of dancing, feasting and music at the Moyo African Village. The 25m long buffet provides an African gastronomic experience of the tastes and flavours of Africa. Get your face painted African style and lucky ISV participants will get to dance up on stage with the local performers!"></a>\r\n		<div class="accordionDescBack"></div>\r\n		<div class="accordionDesc">\r\n			<p class="accordionDescHeader">Cape Town</h3>\r\n			\r\n		</div>                   \r\n	   <div class="slideStrip" title="/img/oap/south_africa/accordion/4strip.jpg"></div>\r\n	   <p class="slideDesc">Cape<br />Town</p>  \r\n	</div>               \r\n	\r\n	<!-- slide 5 -->\r\n	<div id="slide5" class="accordionImgDiv">\r\n		<a href="index.html" id="slideimg5" class="accordionSlideImage asyncImgLoadAccordion" title="/img/oap/south_africa/accordion/5.jpg|Cape Town: Sandboarding|Adrenaline junkies get ready to hit the Atlantis sand dunes, located about an hour from Cape Town. Here you''ll strap on your boots and board and learn how to carve up the dunes with your turns from professionals who pioneered this sport in South Africa. This will be some of the most fun youâ€™ll have on tour, from beginners to experienced riders. The jaw-dropping scenery of white sand dunes and unique views of Table Mountain is a bonus!"></a> \r\n		<div class="accordionDescBack"></div>\r\n		<div class="accordionDesc">\r\n			<p class="accordionDescHeader">Cape Town</h3>\r\n			\r\n		</div>    \r\n		<div class="slideStrip" title="/img/oap/south_africa/accordion/5strip.jpg"></div>\r\n		<p class="slideDesc">Cape<br />Town</p>  \r\n	</div> \r\n	\r\n	<!-- slide 6 -->\r\n	<div id="slide6" class="accordionImgDiv">\r\n		<a href="index.html" id="slideimg6" class="accordionSlideImage asyncImgLoadAccordion" title="/img/oap/south_africa/accordion/6.jpg|Kruger National Park: Sunset Game Drive|In Kruger National Park, sunset is the most magical time of day to explore the bushveld by safari vehicle, looking for African wildlife. This is an amazing opportunity for photography as the sun sets below the horizon, hopefully capturing images of giraffe, elephant, buffalo, lion and other animals that you may not have seen during the morning and afternoon game drives. A not-to-be-missed experience for South Africa!"></a> \r\n		<div class="accordionDescBack"></div>\r\n		<div class="accordionDesc">\r\n			<p class="accordionDescHeader">Kruger National Park</h3>\r\n			\r\n		</div>    \r\n		<div class="slideStrip" title="/img/oap/south_africa/accordion/6strip.jpg"></div>\r\n		<p class="slideDesc">Kruger<br />National <br />Park</p>  \r\n	</div>      \r\n	\r\n</div> <!-- accordionContainer -->\r\n\r\n<!-- ACCORDION CONTROL PANEL -->   \r\n<div id="accordionControlPanel">\r\n<span id="accorControlBtnDesc"></span>\r\n	<img id="accorBackBtn" class="accorControlButton ie6PNGfix" src="img/slider/accordion/control/back.png" alt="" /><img \r\n	id="accorPlayBtn" class="accorControlButton ie6PNGfix" src="img/slider/accordion/control/pause.png" alt="" /><img \r\n	id="accorForwardBtn" class="accorControlButton ie6PNGfix" src="img/slider/accordion/control/forward.png" alt="" /> \r\n</div> <!-- accordionControlPanel -->    \r\n	\r\n	<div id="ImageTitle">Jeffreys Bay: Surfing Lessons</div>\r\n	<div id="ImageDescrip">Learn to surf from local expert instructors in a world renowned location for surfing. This two hour lesson will teach you the basics and hopefully have you &quot;hanging ten&quot; in no time.</div>\r\n</div>			', '', '2010-06-01 18:01:58', '2010-06-01 18:01:58', '', '', 0, '', 0);
