(15, 'Optional Activity Package', 'Optional Activity Package - Thailand', 'h46h45h4', '<h3>About</h3>\r\n\r\n<p class="about">\r\n	The purpose of the Optional Activity Package (OAP) is to provide you with even more activities to enrich your experience in Thailand. We are able to receive excellent prices for these activities, much less expensive than what you could receive if you booked on your own. In addition, the booking will be taken care of for you by your ISV staff so all you have to do is show up and be ready for some adventure! Each year, more than 90% of all ISV participants enjoy the benefits of the Optional Activity Package. Please note that this OAP is offered in addition to the 5 included ISV Activities.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<div id="contents" class="twocolumn">\r\n\r\n	<h2>The Thailand OAP includes:</h2>\r\n	\r\n<!-- ACCORDION IMAGE ROTATOR -->\r\n<div id="js-accordion">\r\n\r\n	<!-- slide 1 -->\r\n	<div id="slide1" class="accordionImgDiv">\r\n		<a href="index.html" id="slideimg1" class="accordionSlideImage asyncImgLoadAccordion" title="/img/oap/thailand/accordion/1.jpg|White Water Rafting â€“ Mae Taeng River|Ride the rapids on the Mae Taeng River in Thailandâ€™s North. Our expert river guides will guide you through some of the challenging class 3 - 4 rapids with stunning local scenery and landscapes."></a>\r\n		<div class="accordionDescBack"></div>\r\n		<div class="accordionDesc">\r\n			<p class="accordionDescHeader">White Water Rafting</h3>\r\n			\r\n		</div>                    \r\n		<div class="slideStrip" title="/img/oap/thailand/accordion/1strip.jpg"></div>\r\n		<p class="slideDesc">White<br />Water<br />Rafting</p>  \r\n	</div>\r\n											  \r\n	<!-- slide 2 -->\r\n	<div id="slide2" class="accordionImgDiv"> \r\n		<a href="index.html" id="slideimg2" class="accordionSlideImage asyncImgLoadAccordion" title="/img/oap/thailand/accordion/2.jpg|Thai Cooking School â€“ evening cooking class|Learn to cook up to five authentic Thai dishes! Our local Thai cooking school in Chiang Mai will assist you in learning how to use all the spices and fresh ingredients of traditional Thai recipes. Finish the evening by tasting your newly developed Thai cooking skills!"></a>\r\n		<div class="accordionDescBack"></div>\r\n		<div class="accordionDesc">\r\n			<p class="accordionDescHeader">Thai Cooking School</h3>\r\n			\r\n		</div>                    \r\n		<div class="slideStrip" title="/img/oap/thailand/accordion/2strip.jpg"></div>\r\n		<p class="slideDesc">Thai<br/>Cooking<br />School</p> \r\n	</div>\r\n					\r\n	<!-- slide 3 -->\r\n	<div id="slide3" class="accordionImgDiv">\r\n		<a href="index.html" id="slideimg3" class="accordionSlideImage asyncImgLoadAccordion" title="/img/oap/thailand/accordion/3.jpg|Traditional Thai Massage|Enjoy a very relaxing Traditional Thai Massage in a professional massage centre. The massage centre caters to large numbers of people with massage chairs and tables in an open setting. An authentic Thai experience."></a>\r\n		<div class="accordionDescBack"></div>\r\n		<div class="accordionDesc">\r\n			<p class="accordionDescHeader">Massage</h3>\r\n			\r\n		</div>                    \r\n		<div class="slideStrip" title="/img/oap/thailand/accordion/3strip.jpg"></div>\r\n		<p class="slideDesc">Massage</p>  \r\n	</div>\r\n							  \r\n	<!-- slide 4 -->\r\n	<div id="slide4" class="accordionImgDiv">\r\n		<a href="index.html" id="slideimg4" class="accordionSlideImage asyncImgLoadAccordion" title="/img/oap/thailand/accordion/4.jpg|Bangkok Discovery Sightseeing|Explore by long-tail boat the khlongs, homes and lifestyles of Bangkok''s waterways. Visit the impressive Wat Phra Kaew & Grand Palace. Also known as the â€œTemple of the Emerald Buddhaâ€, Wat Phra Kaew adjoins the Grand Palace, the former residence of the Thai monarch.You will be able to see some of the magnificent sculptures, paintings and treasured artifacts of the Thai Buddhist culture."></a>\r\n		<div class="accordionDescBack"></div>\r\n		<div class="accordionDesc">\r\n			<p class="accordionDescHeader">Sightseeing</h3>\r\n			\r\n		</div>                   \r\n	   <div class="slideStrip" title="/img/oap/thailand/accordion/4strip.jpg"></div>\r\n	   <p class="slideDesc">Sightseeing</p>  \r\n	</div>               \r\n	\r\n	<!-- slide 5 -->\r\n	<div id="slide5" class="accordionImgDiv">\r\n		<a href="index.html" id="slideimg5" class="accordionSlideImage asyncImgLoadAccordion" title="/img/oap/thailand/accordion/5.jpg|Khao Sok National Park Lake Tour|Enjoy a full day exploring the magnificent towering cliffs and islands hidden throughout the lake deep in Khao Sok National Park. The jungle that is present all the way to the waters edge is considered to be one of the oldest in the world. You will travel by boat into the hidden inlets, caves and islands within the Lake, which is home to many splendid birds, such as hornbills, gibbons, and some of Thailandâ€™s rare wildlife such as the Asian elephant and leopard."></a> \r\n		<div class="accordionDescBack"></div>\r\n		<div class="accordionDesc">\r\n			<p class="accordionDescHeader">Park Lake Tour</h3>\r\n			\r\n		</div>    \r\n		<div class="slideStrip" title="/img/oap/thailand/accordion/5strip.jpg"></div>\r\n		<p class="slideDesc">Park<br />Lake<br />Tour</p>  \r\n	</div>   \r\n	\r\n</div> <!-- accordionContainer -->\r\n\r\n<!-- ACCORDION CONTROL PANEL -->   \r\n<div id="accordionControlPanel">\r\n<span id="accorControlBtnDesc"></span>\r\n	<img id="accorBackBtn" class="accorControlButton ie6PNGfix" src="img/slider/accordion/control/back.png" alt="" /><img \r\n	id="accorPlayBtn" class="accorControlButton ie6PNGfix" src="img/slider/accordion/control/pause.png" alt="" /><img \r\n	id="accorForwardBtn" class="accorControlButton ie6PNGfix" src="img/slider/accordion/control/forward.png" alt="" /> \r\n</div> <!-- accordionControlPanel -->    \r\n	\r\n	<div id="ImageTitle">White Water Rafting â€“ Mae Taeng River</div>\r\n	<div id="ImageDescrip">Ride the rapids on the Mae Taeng River in Thailandâ€™s North. Our expert river guides will guide you through some of the challenging class 3 - 4 rapids with stunning local scenery and landscapes.</div>\r\n</div>			', '', '2010-06-01 18:02:16', '2010-06-01 18:02:16', '', '', 0, '', 0),
(16, 'Optional Activity Package', 'Optional Activity Package - Costa Rica', '45h45h45', '<h3>About</h3>\r\n\r\n<p class="about">\r\n	In addition to the five included activities in the ISV Costa Rica adventure tour, ISV is pleased to offer participants traveling to Costa Rica this exciting Optional Activity Package (OAP). These activities are more of the best that Costa Rica has to offer in outdoor adventure and appreciation of the spectacular natural surroundings. Each year about 95% of participants choose the ISV Optional Activity Package as it adds such great value to the overall experience. All activities in the package will be organized by ISV staff prior to arrival, which ensures availability so that a participant wonâ€™t miss out. All participants have to do is show up and be ready to have a great time!\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<div id="contents" class="twocolumn">\r\n\r\n	<h2>The ISV Costa Rican OAP includes:</h2>\r\n	\r\n<!-- ACCORDION IMAGE ROTATOR -->\r\n<div id="js-accordion">\r\n\r\n	<!-- slide 1 -->\r\n	<div id="slide1" class="accordionImgDiv">\r\n		<a href="index.html" id="slideimg1" class="accordionSlideImage asyncImgLoadAccordion" title="/img/oap/costa_rica/accordion/1.jpg|Samara Beach: Surfing Lessons|Costa Rica is famous for surfing in Latin America. Hereâ€™s your chance to take lessons from professionals who will teach you everything you need to know to get you &quot;hanging ten&quot;! Surfing is one of ISVâ€™s top rated activities, so donâ€™t miss out!"></a>\r\n		<div class="accordionDescBack"></div>\r\n		<div class="accordionDesc">\r\n			<p class="accordionDescHeader">Samara Beach</h3>\r\n			\r\n		</div>                    \r\n		<div class="slideStrip" title="/img/oap/costa_rica/accordion/1strip.jpg"></div>\r\n		<p class="slideDesc">Samara<br />Beach</p>  \r\n	</div>\r\n											  \r\n	<!-- slide 2 -->\r\n	<div id="slide2" class="accordionImgDiv"> \r\n		<a href="index.html" id="slideimg2" class="accordionSlideImage asyncImgLoadAccordion" title="/img/oap/costa_rica/accordion/2.jpg|Samara Beach: Sea Kayaking|From Samara Beach, enjoy a leisurely paddle by kayak to Isla Chora. Leave your kayaks on the beach, and swim on beautiful clear waters.."></a>\r\n		<div class="accordionDescBack"></div>\r\n		<div class="accordionDesc">\r\n			<p class="accordionDescHeader">Samara Beach</h3>\r\n			\r\n		</div>                    \r\n		<div class="slideStrip" title="/img/oap/costa_rica/accordion/2strip.jpg"></div>\r\n		<p class="slideDesc">Samara<br />Beach</p> \r\n	</div>\r\n					\r\n	<!-- slide 3 -->\r\n	<div id="slide3" class="accordionImgDiv">\r\n		<a href="index.html" id="slideimg3" class="accordionSlideImage asyncImgLoadAccordion" title="/img/oap/costa_rica/accordion/3.jpg|Horseback Riding & Tubing Adventure in RincÃ³n de la Vieja National Park|Explore Rincon de la Vieja National Park with two exciting activities. First, start with a relaxed horseback ride through breathtaking forest and scenic trails. Take a break at the beautiful emerald-green Oropendola Waterfall. After this, get ready for the Rio Negro Tubing Adventure! Ride the river rapids for an hour and a half in your own inflatable inner-tube."></a>\r\n		<div class="accordionDescBack"></div>\r\n		<div class="accordionDesc">\r\n			<p class="accordionDescHeader">RincÃ³n de la Vieja National Park</h3>\r\n			\r\n		</div>                    \r\n		<div class="slideStrip" title="/img/oap/costa_rica/accordion/3strip.jpg"></div>\r\n		<p class="slideDesc">RincÃ³n <br />de la <br/>Vieja <br />National <br />Park</p>  \r\n	</div>\r\n							  \r\n	<!-- slide 4 -->\r\n	<div id="slide4" class="accordionImgDiv">\r\n		<a href="index.html" id="slideimg4" class="accordionSlideImage asyncImgLoadAccordion" title="/img/oap/costa_rica/accordion/4.jpg|Guided Hike to Las Pailas Trail & Simbiosis Mud Spa|Visit one of the most famous national parks in all of Costa Rica. Take a guided trek for two hours walk along Las Pailas Trail. The naturalist guide will explain the geothermal wonders such as boiling mud, sulphur lagoons, geysers and natural steam baths. They will also help you spot all the wildlife! Finish this fantastic day at the unique Simbiosis Mud Spa. Enjoy a mud bath from natural mud from the hot boiling ponds, and then bathe in thermal springs, hidden in the middle of the forest"></a>\r\n		<div class="accordionDescBack"></div>\r\n		<div class="accordionDesc">\r\n			<p class="accordionDescHeader">Guided Hike</h3>\r\n			\r\n		</div>                   \r\n	   <div class="slideStrip" title="/img/oap/costa_rica/accordion/4strip.jpg"></div>\r\n	   <p class="slideDesc">Guided <br />Hike</p>  \r\n	</div>               \r\n	\r\n	<!-- slide 5 -->\r\n	<div id="slide5" class="accordionImgDiv">\r\n		<a href="index.html" id="slideimg5" class="accordionSlideImage asyncImgLoadAccordion" title="/img/oap/costa_rica/accordion/5.jpg|Arenal Volcano Evening Hot Springs|Soothe and soak sore muscles as you relax in natural hot springs at night.  As one of the largest attractions of the area, the thermal pools range in temperature and are surrounded by beautiful vegetation. There are waterfalls and a swim-up bar for ice-cold refreshments.  With luck you will see natureâ€™s fireworks as Volcan Arenal erupts in the distance from the comfort of the pools"></a> \r\n		<div class="accordionDescBack"></div>\r\n		<div class="accordionDesc">\r\n			<p class="accordionDescHeader">Hot Springs</h3>\r\n			\r\n		</div>    \r\n		<div class="slideStrip" title="/img/oap/costa_rica/accordion/5strip.jpg"></div>\r\n		<p class="slideDesc">Hot<br />Springs</p>  \r\n	</div> \r\n	\r\n	<!-- slide 6 -->\r\n	<div id="slide6" class="accordionImgDiv">\r\n		<a href="index.html" id="slideimg6" class="accordionSlideImage asyncImgLoadAccordion" title="/img/oap/costa_rica/accordion/6.jpg|Rappel at Arenal Adventure World Ecological Park|Get set for adrenaline and adventure as you rappel down a rushing waterfall! Descending 30 m (90 ft) on a free rappel followed by another 50 m down the Pino Blanco waterfall. This is the largest rappel in Costa Rica and will be an unforgettable experience for those with courage and thirst for adventure!"></a> \r\n		<div class="accordionDescBack"></div>\r\n		<div class="accordionDesc">\r\n			<p class="accordionDescHeader">Rappel</h3>\r\n			\r\n		</div>    \r\n		<div class="slideStrip" title="/img/oap/costa_rica/accordion/6strip.jpg"></div>\r\n		<p class="slideDesc">Rappel</p>  \r\n	</div>      \r\n	\r\n</div> <!-- accordionContainer -->\r\n\r\n<!-- ACCORDION CONTROL PANEL -->   \r\n<div id="accordionControlPanel">\r\n<span id="accorControlBtnDesc"></span>\r\n	<img id="accorBackBtn" class="accorControlButton ie6PNGfix" src="img/slider/accordion/control/back.png" alt="" /><img \r\n	id="accorPlayBtn" class="accorControlButton ie6PNGfix" src="img/slider/accordion/control/pause.png" alt="" /><img \r\n	id="accorForwardBtn" class="accorControlButton ie6PNGfix" src="img/slider/accordion/control/forward.png" alt="" /> \r\n</div> <!-- accordionControlPanel -->       \r\n	\r\n	<div id="ImageTitle">Samara Beach: Surfing Lessons</div>\r\n	<div id="ImageDescrip">Costa Rica is famous for surfing in Latin America. Hereâ€™s your chance to take lessons from professionals who will teach you everything you need to know to get you &quot;hanging ten&quot;! Surfing is one of ISVâ€™s top rated activities, so donâ€™t miss out!</div>\r\n</div>			', '', '2010-06-01 18:02:38', '2010-06-01 18:02:38', '', '', 0, '', 0),
(17, 'Optional Activity Package', 'Optional Activity Package - Eastern Europe', '34g34g', '<h3>About</h3>\r\n\r\n<p class="about">\r\n	In addition to the five included activities in the ISV Eastern Europe Adventure Tour, ISV is pleased to offer participants traveling to Eastern Europe this exciting Optional Activity Package (OAP). These activities are more of the best that Eastern Europe has to offer in outdoor adventure and appreciation of the spectacular natural and cultural surroundings. Each year about 95% of participants choose the ISV Optional Activity Package as it adds such great value to the overall experience. All activities in the package will be organized by ISV staff prior to arrival, which ensures availability so that a participant won''t miss out. All participants have to do is show up and be ready to have a great time! \r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<div id="contents" class="twocolumn">\r\n\r\n	<h2>The ISV Eastern Europe OAP includes:</h2>\r\n	\r\n<!-- ACCORDION IMAGE ROTATOR -->\r\n<div id="js-accordion">\r\n\r\n	<!-- slide 1 -->\r\n	<div id="slide1" class="accordionImgDiv">\r\n		<a href="index.html" id="slideimg1" class="accordionSlideImage asyncImgLoadAccordion" title="/img/oap/eastern_europe/accordion/1.jpg|Caving|Slovenia contains some of the largest cave systems in Europe and this caving adventure will take you deep into underground karst systems where only the light of our headlamps can penetrate. Winding passageways lead to caverns adorned with stalagmites and stalactites, their crystals glittering under our lights. With our experienced guides, we will walk, crawl and rappel our way through this unique environment to be born again when sun hits us upon our exit to the outside world."></a>\r\n		<div class="accordionDescBack"></div>\r\n		<div class="accordionDesc">\r\n			<p class="accordionDescHeader">Caving</h3>\r\n			\r\n		</div>                    \r\n		<div class="slideStrip" title="/img/oap/eastern_europe/accordion/1strip.jpg"></div>\r\n		<p class="slideDesc">Caving</p>  \r\n	</div>\r\n											  \r\n	<!-- slide 2 -->\r\n	<div id="slide2" class="accordionImgDiv"> \r\n		<a href="index.html" id="slideimg2" class="accordionSlideImage asyncImgLoadAccordion" title="/img/oap/eastern_europe/accordion/2.jpg|Lake Bled Castle and Bike Tour|This idyllic glacial lake, complete with 15th Century church nestled on an island, and medieval castle clinging to a rockface, has a hypnotic beauty which has enticed travelers seeking rest and relaxation since the 11th century. On your tour you will circumnavigate the lake on bicycle, stopping for lunch and a refreshing dip in the lakes emerald waters. Then, walking atop the cliff for amazing views across the lake, you enter one of Sloveniaâ€™s the oldest castles featuring Romanesque towers and Baroque architecture. With the imposing Julian Alps as a backdrop, this day is the perfect introduction to mountain life in Slovenia."></a>\r\n		<div class="accordionDescBack"></div>\r\n		<div class="accordionDesc">\r\n			<p class="accordionDescHeader">Lake Bled Castle</h3>\r\n			\r\n		</div>                    \r\n		<div class="slideStrip" title="/img/oap/eastern_europe/accordion/2strip.jpg"></div>\r\n		<p class="slideDesc">Lake Bled<br />Castle</p> \r\n	</div>\r\n					\r\n	<!-- slide 3 -->\r\n	<div id="slide3" class="accordionImgDiv">\r\n		<a href="index.html" id="slideimg3" class="accordionSlideImage asyncImgLoadAccordion" title="/img/oap/eastern_europe/accordion/3.jpg|Centina River Canyoning|Experience the adrenaline rush of rappelling down the beautiful limestone cliffs of the Cetina River canyon. Once on the river, the adrenaline continues as we splash through rapids, jump from ledges and navigate the more difficult sections of our descent down the river by zip-line. After more swimming and floating in crystal clear pools we rappel another section to get to the &quot;big jump.&quot; Whatever your level of experience, this activity has something for everyone and in the summer heat, the Cetina River is definitely the place to be!"></a>\r\n		<div class="accordionDescBack"></div>\r\n		<div class="accordionDesc">\r\n			<p class="accordionDescHeader">Centina River</h3>\r\n			\r\n		</div>                    \r\n		<div class="slideStrip" title="/img/oap/eastern_europe/accordion/3strip.jpg"></div>\r\n		<p class="slideDesc">Centina<br/>River</p>  \r\n	</div>\r\n							  \r\n	<!-- slide 4 -->\r\n	<div id="slide4" class="accordionImgDiv">\r\n		<a href="index.html" id="slideimg4" class="accordionSlideImage asyncImgLoadAccordion" title="/img/oap/eastern_europe/accordion/4.jpg|Omis Rock Climbing|It''s time to enter a vertical world as we explore the limestone cliffs of Omis! Set amidst an amazing mountain backdrop, we will be instructed in the intricacies of rock craft as we scale to great heights. Also test your nerve on a series of rappels (descending a fixed line) â€“ the ultimate challenge is 150ft high!"></a>\r\n		<div class="accordionDescBack"></div>\r\n		<div class="accordionDesc">\r\n			<p class="accordionDescHeader">Omis</h3>\r\n			\r\n		</div>                   \r\n	   <div class="slideStrip" title="/img/oap/eastern_europe/accordion/4strip.jpg"></div>\r\n	   <p class="slideDesc">Omis</p>  \r\n	</div>               \r\n	\r\n	<!-- slide 5 -->\r\n	<div id="slide5" class="accordionImgDiv">\r\n		<a href="index.html" id="slideimg5" class="accordionSlideImage asyncImgLoadAccordion" title="/img/oap/eastern_europe/accordion/5.jpg|Korcula Island Culture|It''s time to enter a vertical world as we explore the limestone cliffs of Omis! Set amidst an amazing mountain backdrop, we will be instructed in the intricacies of rock craft as we scale to great heights. Also test your nerve on a series of rappels (descending a fixed line) â€“ the ultimate challenge is 150ft high!"></a> \r\n		<div class="accordionDescBack"></div>\r\n		<div class="accordionDesc">\r\n			<p class="accordionDescHeader">Korcula</h3>\r\n			\r\n		</div>    \r\n		<div class="slideStrip" title="/img/oap/eastern_europe/accordion/5strip.jpg"></div>\r\n		<p class="slideDesc">Korcula<br />Island</p>  \r\n	</div>   \r\n	\r\n</div> <!-- accordionContainer -->\r\n\r\n<!-- ACCORDION CONTROL PANEL -->   \r\n<div id="accordionControlPanel">\r\n<span id="accorControlBtnDesc"></span>\r\n	<img id="accorBackBtn" class="accorControlButton ie6PNGfix" src="img/slider/accordion/control/back.png" alt="" /><img \r\n	id="accorPlayBtn" class="accorControlButton ie6PNGfix" src="img/slider/accordion/control/pause.png" alt="" /><img \r\n	id="accorForwardBtn" class="accorControlButton ie6PNGfix" src="img/slider/accordion/control/forward.png" alt="" /> \r\n</div> <!-- accordionControlPanel -->  \r\n	\r\n	<div id="ImageTitle">Caving</div>\r\n	<div id="ImageDescrip">Slovenia contains some of the largest cave systems in Europe and this caving adventure will take you deep into underground karst systems where only the light of our headlamps can penetrate. Winding passageways lead to caverns adorned with stalagmites and stalactites, their crystals glittering under our lights. With our experienced guides, we will walk, crawl and rappel our way through this unique environment to be born again when sun hits us upon our exit to the outside world.</div>\r\n</div>			', '', '2010-06-01 18:02:54', '2010-06-01 18:02:54', '', '', 0, '', 0),
